{
  "stem": "6989.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like-- I don't remember ever doing anything except [? in ?] that [? whole ?] [? thought ?] that I told you, that you know--",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--with the cows and butter and things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just remember seeing it and knowing what it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know how, what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess they must have said something, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Between them.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only thing that she wanted to do is talk Jewish to me at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't want to be Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to hear anything Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I didn't know religiously, Christian.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I sort of became Lena's daughter, I guess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was, already, towards the end, when we weren't so afraid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we knew, already, the war was coming and the Germans were retreating.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in fact, one of the pictures I think that you have, that I showed you, is in front of a church.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember going to church.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Is-- In fact, after we were liberated I went to church even more.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember-- I don't know, it must have-- I must have been there in December or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I remember decorating the tree with them and being very excited about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was already after the Germans left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did go to church.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in fact, after the liberation of this town-- it wasn't the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were a lot of young boys killed from mines, where they either stepped on it or picked it up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember going to wakes and being very, very scared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very, very scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I had to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
